{
  "stem": "22972.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father came back in a week and he got a very, very plain bracelet that-- and the man said to him, I coated it with junk on top, but it's solid gold-- heavy, heavy, heavy-- as dense as I could get this wonderful, pure, pure, 24 whatever karat gold that my father had collected.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we finally-- we left that-- my mother wore that bracelet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He wore the belt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She wore the bracelet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a nothing looking bracelet on the outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very wide, but it was matte finish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Didn't look like anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We left it in England, and when we finally got to America, our friends sent us that bracelet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when-- when my father took it to 47th Street to have it appraised, and the man that he gave it to looked at the bracelet and said, what do you want with this?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said, it's 24 karat gold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's melted down, pure gold krugerrands, whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, no it isn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he scratched it, and it was nothing but iron underneath.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is how the Germans cheated us until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nevertheless, I mean, Germans came to America by hook or by crook, and they became maids, and butlers, and they sold the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our furniture-- as you look around-- I live in a museum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have things that have been in my family for 300 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The boat that our furniture and everything came out on, literally, was the last boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After that, if you wanted to take-- this chair, for instance.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
